  <h1>Welcome to My Dog Blog!</h1>
  <h2>Page 1: Fun Facts about Dogs</h2>
  <p>Here are some interesting facts about dogs:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Dogs are descendants of wolves.</li>
    <li>They have an incredible sense of smell.</li>
    <li>Dogs come in a wide variety of breeds, each with its own unique characteristics.</li>
    <li>They are known for their loyalty and companionship.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Page 2: Caring for Your Dog</h2>
  <p>Here are some tips for taking care of your furry friend:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Provide a balanced and nutritious diet.</li>
    <li>Make sure your dog gets regular exercise.</li>
    <li>Groom your dog regularly, including brushing their fur and trimming their nails.</li>
    <li>Train and socialize your dog to ensure good behavior.</li>
    <li>Don't forget about regular visits to the veterinarian for check-ups and vaccinations.</li>
  </ol>

